Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:41.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇と遊ぶ星たちへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛を歌い　飽きつくした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏を灯し　雛菊の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:56.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に寄り添う爪の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:04.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唇から唇へと伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その温もりはどこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:15.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿り付くあてはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:21.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたでなくちゃ　満たせない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:25.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私じゃなきゃ　許せなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:30.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　私はこの足で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がれて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぞっとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼い殺しなら　救われる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:44.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも見事に　鍵は外れて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:55.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私はまるで　鳥籠を欲している狂う籠鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:04:03.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘を抱いた花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:41.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗游戏的星斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱咏唱　我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮夏季的雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:56.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随梦境的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:04.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过双唇传递而来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份温存将何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:15.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有可以前往的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:21.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你　我得不到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:25.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我　是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:30.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能用自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却感到心惊胆寒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果养我一生　我还可以得救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:44.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　锁却顺利打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:55.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宛如为渴求鸟笼而疯狂的笼中之鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:04:03.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱谎言的花

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[ED]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てて　ご覧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:01.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　満ちぬけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:06.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溢れた傍から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:11.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えて　抜け殻に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:21.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流されて　辿り付く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:27.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現　蕩ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:33.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天この魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:44.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢　紡いだ夢を　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:53.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その小指に絡めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:57.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛んだ刺は
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:03.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一つ抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取る　抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:01.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊　充满了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:06.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从溢出的一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:11.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐消失　变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:21.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随波逐流　到达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:27.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉于现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:33.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:44.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦　编织的梦境　请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:53.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请缠绕我的小指不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:57.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:03.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根被拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出　拔掉

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山河三岔路 别离之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护的是自己 是他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是常世的黑暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非对错无法补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有终结的深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭转时空 打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难报之怨 我为您报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧杯碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把烧杯打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我撞到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 是我撞到学姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用争了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑和御影以后都要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 遇到位好老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没见过新山老师生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 这就是大人的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是学生干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她很诚实地道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就没批评她 原谅她了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑是个乖孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习态度也很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父母一定很可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是新山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 您找哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂

Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把她带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是1年A班片濑莉莉香的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有别的话要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师 听说你昨天批评了片濑 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我没有批
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉香说你把学姐打破的烧杯赖在她头上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长对教师这种蛮横无礼的行为不闻不问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 决没有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果确实有这样的事情发生 我一定严格处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是如果 这样的事情已经实际发生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 我没有批评过片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 你还想抵赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你应该先道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 在这里就担起身为教师的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的行为引起了误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始这么说不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恬不知耻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她终于回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师 真是飞来横祸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种监护人多起来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算心中不服 也要先低头道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 放学以后我先问问片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要多加小心 不要刺激学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要温和 温和地问她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 奶奶来说了那样的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母误会老师是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶一生气起来 就非常可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可以麻烦片濑和奶奶说说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有 一点点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的样子 相当愤怒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所谓的「Monster Parents」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙比怪物还麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说比怪物还可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我们说成这样 人做成这样也太失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您找谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真自我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢问 是片濑的奶奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接电话的时候 不应该先报自己的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样也算教师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑夫人 能不能请您冷静地听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是最了解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 教师对监护人叫「你」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道现在几点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和时间没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是教师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己伤害了学生的心 却打着呼噜大睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个自我主义的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有伤害您孙女的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你把莉莉香叫过去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她对我说你是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然威胁学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁 您在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打碎烧杯的不是三年级学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为中考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让她进好高中 不想给她的履历留下污点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就把问题推给低年级学生了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的肮脏想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有你这种异常教师在的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把莉莉香送进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当一段时间 我不会让她去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异常的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 哪里 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从学校的角度来说 这次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚开始一直那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会和老师好好谈谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}蛮横教师 不可原谅\N赛河原四中的理科教师\N新山美和\N将虚有的罪名施加于学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们只向着自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起孩子 更担心自己的安危吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 没有这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑夫人 请冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冷静啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个教师交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许她推卸责任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦的不止是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把校长叫来 叫校长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告到教师委员会去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑莉莉香自从父母死于车祸以来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直由那位外祖母抚养至今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她特别疼爱莉莉香 这个我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到会到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑又没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说如果不开除新山老师 就不让孩子上学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问过片濑曾经就读的东京小学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:13:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位老太太果然是个危险人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她对我这个班主任倒没露出那种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是她们八字不合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和新山老师的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位小学的老师似乎也一直以低姿态等台风过境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把事情闹得太大 可能会伤害到其他学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为教师 必须避免这样的事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新山老师 我们都知道这次的事情错不在你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都支持你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 当前还是忍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我们团结一心 一起渡过这个难关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 片濑的奶奶说其实是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是个意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有人却想把别人说成坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师什么时候变成这种职业了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事 都不能说真话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道是错的 也必须点头称是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这些告诉在公司工作的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说到了社会上 这些是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我认为 教授在现实中生存的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与教授理想是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为 教师一定要生存在理想世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪 人都是活在现实里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这次的事情 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至怀疑 学生和老师是不是都只考虑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你帮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就到片濑家 和老太太谈一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了 你回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拧一下 拧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师真成了不幸的职业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也绝对不要当老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨女和一目连真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从不同的意义上讲 那也是个不幸的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拧一下 拧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要转多少圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很容易受伤 所以总是把事情想得很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果不把谁看成敌人 她就无法安心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其实是个很好的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢 给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告你非法侵入哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑夫人 请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉香 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说你什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说如果不让奶奶住口的话 又要欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧 给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不那么说的话 我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能把事实告诉奶奶的 只有你这个亲人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于你说谎而被骂的老师会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是老师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老师是大人 所以无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山童
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的想报怨 就解开这根红线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会下地狱 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到谣言了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为是教师而受人摆布 我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家都说我是教师 非要把我逼入绝境的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想作为教师复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师必须对其负责的不是监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 随便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 由我来消除

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[预告]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹泽夕菜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那个老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.53,0:24:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在老师身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望老师只看我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那家伙总是妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍眼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.87,0:24:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙 死了才好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 我的老师
